reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 10, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I was nervous about size so went with this one. It’s slightly smaller than the 22x14x9 requirement for Delta. I think it stands 20in tall and is 14x9. It fit in the larger Delta plane and the small two seater plane. Rolls amazingly. Pulls great. Very sturdy. Holds more than you think. It’s not expandable, but that’s okay cause it would be over the limit if you did expand it. Had TSA lock. Overall, great carry on. Cool looking too!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 9, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Just used it for a work travel. Held 4 days of travel/work clothes along with 2 days of gym clothes. Did have to store a pair of shoes and makeup bad elsewhere. It does have some give so sat on the floors and really pressed hard to zip. (Really I sat on it to zip it so the zippers are strong) Sturdy and good color.
